Package com.jalios.jcms.extradbdata

Class ExtraDBData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jalios.jcms.extradbdata.ExtraDBData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBData, java.io.Serializable
    public class ExtraDBData
extends java.lang.Object
implements DBData
    Class used to store Data's extra data to hibernate.

    Do not use this class to change extradata values for a data. See Data (possibly ExtraDBDataManager).

    Since:
    jcms-6.0
